    {
      "Type": "Paragraph",
      "Content": "Ryo is a 17-year-old boy that serves as the story's deuteragonist and supporting character. Growing up in the rough edges of Northern Manila and in the town of Pook-Tulay, he is treated by the citizens of the town as its protector. A skilled physical protector, he keeps the townspeople of Pook-Tulay from dangerous gangs and organizations, big or small, with a nice and violent conversation of his fists."
    },
    {
