    {
      "Type": "Bulleted_List",
      "Header": "Pahinata Crew",
      "Content": "The Pahinata Crew, comprised of Kenji Castillo, Anjerica Navarro, and Kyoji Sarmiento, is Ryo's main circle of friends.\nOriginally treating them as coworkers, Ryo slowly began to see them as his closest friends, despite their stark difference in attitude and personalities.\nDuring vacant times and after hours of classes, Ryo works at the Pahinata Bookstore as a cashier.\nWhenever there is a major threat in town, him and the crew would often meet at the bookstore's office after hours to attack the threat and protect the town as a group.\nGiven his sharp and street-smart strategical prowess, he often devises the strategies the crew does during these situations."
